Sample_ID	- The ID of the individual moray eel followed by the 1 to 2 letter abbreviation of the GI tract location
ID - The ID of the individual moray eel
Crustacean Present - Whether or not there was a crustacean found in the GI tract of the moray individual
GI_tract_location - 3 regions for the small intestine (Anterior, Middle, and Posterior) and 3 regions for the stomach (Fundus, Body, and Antrum)
Amylase - units = (µmol/(min*g))
Maltase - units = (µmol/(min*g))
Lipase - units = (µmol/(min*g))
NAG - units = (µmol/(min*g))
AP - units = (µmol/(min*g))
Trypsin - units = (µmol/(min*g))
Amino_Peptidase - units = (µmol/(min*g))
Chitinase - units = (µmol/(min*g))
Pepsin - units = (µmol/(min*g))
